(Minime, Chordate is not at the battle, it's Choran.  And Logomorph, the 
rockets Anubis and Hades are firing are not seekers)

Anubis/Hades/Predator/Choran/Serpentor:



Anubis fired two optic blasts off at the fying Shadow Wing.

Hades chuckled, jumping into the air several feet high, landing to the 
ground, Spears missing him.  He turned, firing a rocket off at Spears in her 
current mode.

===

Predator ducked, a blast sending him slamming into a tree.  He raised his 
weapon, firing a grenade off at Rex's chest.

---

Choran sidestepped, letting Brix jump by him.  Laughing, Choran fired 15 
rapid laser bolts off at the middle of Brix's back.

===

Serpentor landed on his skid plate, a knife from subspace appearing in his 
left hand, soon flying at Striker's chest, three plasma bolts following.
